🇬🇳#Guinea in west #Africa received a donation of 200,000 #Sinopharm #COVID19 #vaccine doses from #China on 3rd March, as it seeks help from multiple sources to halt the spread of the coronavirus.
Chinese Amb. HUANG Wei handed over the vaccines. @chine_guinee @LansanaK_GN https://t.co/Bpo76Bts5i
